 of marmalade (see tip), then leave to cool for 10 minutes. Pour into warm, sterilised jars and seal immediately. Label before storing in a cool, dry place. Once opened, store in fridge."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Setting point test: place a saucer in the freezer (5-10 minutes). Place 1 tsp marmalade onto the saucer. When cool, push marmalade with your finger. If it wrinkles, it is ready. If not, boil for a further <strong>3 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/strong>, then test again."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","2h 30m","1 total recipe"]}